me.pavva.pokejava.Move

  • Packages that use Move 
    Package Description
    me.pavva.pokejava
    Contains the classes required for the main game code including the setup, logic, Move and Pokemon Classes, and Type Enum.
    me.pavva.pokejava.moves
    me.pavva.pokejava.moves contains all the moves programmed into the game, organized by Type, into one of the 17 [TYPE]Moves.java classes.
